{
  "chapter": 38,
  "chapter_summary": "第三十八回 江南大侠。小鱼儿在酒楼饱餐一顿后，玉面神判萧子春露出真面目，率众围杀小鱼儿，声称受人之托取其性命。小鱼儿被困重围，与江玉郎相连无法逃脱，处境危急。关键时刻，\"恶赌鬼\"轩辕三光从天而降，以惊人武功击退鬼影子何无双等人，震慑全场。轩辕三光逼迫江玉郎赌命，江玉郎吓得魂飞魄散。此时江南大侠江别鹤翩然登场，主动代替儿子与轩辕三光对赌。江别鹤以精妙掌法击穿梨木桌面而不溅出鱼翅羹一滴，轩辕三光自叹不如当场认输，表示任凭江别鹤处置。本章展现了各方势力的角力与人物性格：小鱼儿的机智从容、轩辕三光的豪迈霸道、江别鹤的深不可测。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "肚兄肚兄，今日我总算对得起你了吧！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 2,
      "line_end": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_zi_chun",
      "speaker_name": "玉面神判",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "酒菜都已够了么？可要再用些瓜果？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_xiao_zi_chun",
      "text": "我很想，只是肚子却不答应。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_zi_chun",
      "speaker_name": "玉面神判",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "既是如此，我等总算不负神锡道长之托，已尽过地主之谊了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_xiao_zi_chun",
      "text": "你话里好像有话……",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_zi_chun",
      "speaker_name": "玉面神判",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "阁下不妨先推开窗子看看。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这算什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_zi_chun",
      "speaker_name": "玉面神判",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "受人之托，忠人之事，神锡道长托我好生招待于你，我等便尽了地主之谊。但还有一人，却托我等来取你的头颅，你看怎样？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_xiao_zi_chun",
      "text": "我这颗脑袋居然还有人要，这倒真是荣幸之至，但要我脑袋的这人又是准？你总该说来听听。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_zi_chun",
      "speaker_name": "玉面神判",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你只需知道他有一个鼻子两只眼睛已足够了。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "看来，今天我只得将脑袋送给你们了……一盆蜜汁火腿就换去了我的脑袋，这岂非太便宜了些！",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_di",
      "speaker_name": "李迪",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你还要我等动手么？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_li_di",
      "text": "用不着了，只是不知道你的刀快不快？若是一刀保险可以切下脑袋，我倒想借来用用。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_di",
      "speaker_name": "李迪",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "好，念你死到临头，还有谈笑的本事，某家就把这柄刀借给你。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_zi_chun",
      "speaker_name": "玉面神判",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你为何不拔？你拔出这柄刀来，就可以一刀砍向我，或是别的人，或是将刀架在江玉郎的脖子上，逼我们放走你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_zi_chun",
      "speaker_name": "玉面神判",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你不敢拔这柄刀的，是吗？只因为你自己也知道，只要你拔出这柄刀，只有死得更惨。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_zi_chun",
      "speaker_name": "玉面神判",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "念你是个聪明人，且给你个速死，咄，去吧！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_zi_chun",
      "speaker_name": "玉面神判",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么人？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_zi_chun",
      "speaker_name": "玉面神判",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "这位兄台贵姓大名？为何无端出手伤人？",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_xiao_zi_chun",
      "text": "谁是你的兄台，你是什么玩意儿？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_zi_chun",
      "speaker_name": "萧子春",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "在下萧子春，江湖人称玉面神判。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_xiao_zi_chun",
      "text": "好个响亮的名头，你配么？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_di",
      "speaker_name": "李迪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你……你便是'恶赌鬼'轩辕三光！",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "儿子们眼见老子来了，怎地还不快摆上酒菜！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_di",
      "speaker_name": "李迪",
      "listener": "char_dian_xiao_huo",
      "text": "小二，瞧见老子来了，为何还不摆上菜来。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁要你斟酒？除了对面两个姓江的娃儿，全给老子远远站开。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "喝！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "你可知道这酒叫什么酒？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "弟……弟子愚昧，实在不懂。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "这一杯叫赌酒，无论谁喝了老子倒的酒，都得和老子赌一赌。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "怎么？你不赌？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "吐……吐……吐……",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "好，你龟儿子要赌啥？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "吐……吐什么……都可以。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "好，老子就赌你这条手臂。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "你怕什么？反正也未必一定输的。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "坐直了，说，你要怎样赌？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "轩辕先生若要赌，在下可以奉陪，寻这等黄口孺子来赌，岂非无趣么？",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "text": "你是谁？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "在下江别鹤。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "text": "江湖传言，江南一带，出了个了不起的英雄，乃是燕南天之后第一个当得起'大侠'两字的人物，莫非就是你？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "那只是江湖朋友抬爱，在下怎担当得起。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "text": "虎父犬子……虎父犬子……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "text": "他既是你儿子，你莫非要代他与我赌一赌？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "轩辕先生若有兴致，在下自当奉陪。不知轩辕先生赌注如何？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "text": "你我俩人无论谁输了，便任凭对方处置！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "就是这样也好，但如何赌法，还请见告。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "text": "好，江南大侠果然豪气干云，我定了赌注，如何赌法便由得你，这是我的规矩。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "既是如此，在下恭敬不如从命了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "text": "这又算什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "你我依次往桌上击一掌，谁若将这碗鱼翅震得溅出，或是使得碗落下去，那人便算输了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "你我一掌击下，必定穿透桌面，是以就算你我俩人都未将这碗鱼翅羹震倒，到了后来，桌面上俱是掌痕，那中央一块，总要落下去的，谁击下最后一掌，谁就输了，是以桌子越小，胜负便越早。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这样的赌法，倒真连我也未曾见过。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "在下已击下了第一掌，此刻该轮到轩辕先生了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "text": "我'恶赌鬼'平生与人大赌小赌，不下万次，从未有一次还未赌时，便已先认输了……但这次，我不必赌，已认输了……我掌力纵能穿透桌面，却万万不能令这碗见鬼的鱼翅羹一滴也不溅出来。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "speaker_name": "轩辕三光",
      "listener": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "text": "现在，你要我怎样，只管说吧！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 38,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yuan_san_guang",
      "text": "在下且敬轩辕先生一杯。",
